  "rationale": "<p>The value of <i>f</i>(0) is the <i>y</i>-coordinate of the point on the graph where <i>x</i> = 0. The graph crosses the <i>y</i>-axis at (0, 9), so <i>f</i>(0) = 9.</p>",
